import React from 'react'
import { Container, Formwrap } from './signinelements'

const SignIn = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Container>
                <Formwrap>
                    <Icon to='/'>dolla</Icon>
                    <Formcontext></Formcontext>
                </Formwrap>
            </Container>
        </>
    )
}

export default SignIn
